<div class="faq-page">
  <div class="faq-header">
    <span class="section-label">Got Questions</span>
    <h1 class="faq-title">Everything You<br><em>Need to Know</em></h1>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-list">

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        Does gua sha actually work?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Yes — if you do it consistently. Gua sha physically moves fluid in your lymphatic system and stimulates facial muscles. The results are cumulative. Most customers notice reduced puffiness from the first week. Jawline definition becomes visible around weeks 2–3. Skin texture improvements build over months of daily use.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        How long does it take to see results?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p><strong>Reduced morning puffiness:</strong> 1–3 days.<br>
        <strong>Visible jawline definition:</strong> 2–3 weeks of daily use.<br>
        <strong>Skin texture and tone:</strong> 4–8 weeks.<br><br>
        The key is consistency — 5 minutes every morning, not 30 minutes once a week.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        Do I need to use the facial oil?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We strongly recommend it. Gua sha on dry skin drags and can cause friction — which defeats the purpose. The facial oil creates the glide the stone needs and amplifies results because your skin is primed to absorb active ingredients immediately after a session. If you don't have our oil, use your regular moisturiser or a few drops of any facial oil.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        Can I use gua sha if I have acne?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Yes — with care. Avoid active breakouts (pimples, cysts, inflamed spots). Work around them. Gua sha can actually help with overall skin clarity over time by improving circulation and lymphatic drainage. If you have severe cystic acne, speak to a dermatologist first.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        How do I clean my gua sha stone?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>After each use, rinse gently with mild soap and cool water — avoid hot water, which can crack natural stone. Let it air dry on a clean cloth. Never soak your stone or put it in the dishwasher.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        How often should I do the ritual?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Every morning. The lymphatic system responds to consistent, daily stimulation. Sporadic use gives sporadic results. 5 minutes every morning is the practice that creates change.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        Is gua sha safe for all skin types?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Yes — including sensitive skin. Use light pressure, always move upward and outward, and never use on broken, sunburned, or actively inflamed skin.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        What is your return policy?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We offer a 30-Day Ritual Guarantee. Do the ritual every morning for 30 days and if you don't see a difference, contact us for a full refund — no questions asked. For unopened orders, we accept returns within 30 days of delivery.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        Where does my order ship from and how long does it take?
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Orders are processed within 1–2 business days. Standard shipping takes 5–10 business days. Expedited options are available at checkout. You'll receive a tracking number as soon as your order ships.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="faq-cta">
    <p>Still have a question?</p>
    <a href="mailto:hello@rituel.co" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;max-width:240px;text-decoration:none;text-align:center;padding:18px 40px;">
      <span>Contact Us</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.faq-page { padding: 160px 80px 100px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
.faq-header { margin-bottom: 72px; }
.faq-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 68px); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; margin-top: 16px; }
.faq-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--terracotta); }
.faq-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-dark); }
.faq-question {
  width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  padding: 28px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 20px; color: var(--espresso);
  text-align: left; gap: 24px; transition: color 0.3s;
}
.faq-question:hover { color: var(--terracotta); }
.faq-icon { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 300; flex-shrink: 0; transition: transform 0.3s; color: var(--terracotta); line-height: 1; }
.faq-item.open .faq-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); }
.faq-answer { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1), padding 0.3s; }
.faq-item.open .faq-answer { max-height: 400px; padding-bottom: 28px; }
.faq-answer p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.9; color: var(--stone); }
.faq-answer strong { color: var(--espresso); font-weight: 500; }
.faq-cta { margin-top: 80px; padding-top: 80px; border-top: 1px solid var(--cream-dark); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 24px; text-align: center; }
.faq-cta p { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 28px; font-style: italic; color: var(--stone); }
@media (max-width: 1024px) { .faq-page { padding: 140px 40px 80px; } }
</style>

<script>
function toggleFaq(btn) {
  const item = btn.closest('.faq-item');
  const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));
  if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');
}
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "FAQ Page",
  "presets": [{ "name": "FAQ Page" }]
}
{% endschema %}
